1. MAX VALUE of `bso.ttl` in `syncserver(py)`  is 2147483647  (signed int) represents `Tue Jan 19 11:14:07 2038` ,  default VALUE is 2100000000 represents `Fri Jul 18 21:20:00 2036`
2 `syncstorage-rs` currently (at 202109) is not self hostable.
